  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients treated for hyperlipidemia with a HMG-CoA reductase inhibitor (i.e.
             pravastatin, simvastatin rosuvastatin or atorvastatin) and reporting myopathic
             symptoms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with other identifiable cause of myopathy. Patients with clinical evidence of
             hepatic, renal, or endocrine disease; coagulopathy; or other serious medical
             conditions will be excluded.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
